    "wizard_length_select": "Set eo approximate naan count ñan kōṃṃan content. Kālōt from short (200 naan) ñan quick reads ñan deep (2000 naan) ñan comprehensive coverage. Longer texts allow eḷap ḷọk examples im detail.",
