    "persona_panel": "Eo AI Persona chat panel - engage ilo authentic conversations ippan historical figures, scientists, literary characters, ak custom personas. Uses advanced AI ñan simulate period-accurate speech patterns, knowledge, im perspectives. Perfect ñan primary source analysis, perspective-taking, im empathy-building exercises. Supports multiple response modes: Ilo-Character (fully immersive), Educational (ippan learning scaffolds), ak Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "An AI persona ready ñan conversation. kajjojo card shows eo character's āt, iien period, im expertise area. Klik ñan jino an interview - eo AI will respond authentically based ioon their historical context, beliefs, im knowledge. Kōjerbal personas ñan primary source analysis, perspective-taking exercises, ak creative writing inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Generate AI personas automatically from eo am source content. Eo system analyzes eo am text ñan kile key figures, historical periods, ak character archetypes im creates authentic conversational partners. Kōṃṃan personas include accurate biographical details, period-appropriate vocabulary, im contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know about events ālikin their iien).",
    "persona_select_button": "Kālōt in persona ñan begin eo am interview ak conversation. Once selected, kwe'll deḷọñ an immersive chat interface ia kwe maroñ ask kajjitōk, explore their perspective, im earn XP ñan meaningful exchanges. Eo AI responds based ioon eo character's historical knowledge, personality, im cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return ñan eo persona selection screen ñan kālōt a different character. eo am current conversation progress ej automatically saved, im kwe maroñ return ñan wōnṃaanḷọk it later. in allows exploring multiple perspectives ioon eo same historical topic.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Kobaik specific requirements ñan how eo persona should behave during conversations. Examples: focus ioon a specific iien period, emphasize certain beliefs ak values, maintain particular speech patterns, ak limit responses ñan historically accurate knowledge. rūkaki maroñ kōjerbal in ñan align personas ippan specific learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Kālōt how eo persona responds ñan create different learning experiences. IN CHARACTER: Fully immersive historical voice ippan no modern explanations. EDUCATIONAL: Character speaks but includes learning scaffolds, vocabulary support, im context. MIXED: Balanced approach ippan authentic voice plus occasional clarifications. Kālōt based ioon rūkkatak readiness im learning goals.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type eo am own kapeḷḷọk-ended response instead in selecting from pre-written options. Free response mode promotes creative expression, critical thinking, im authentic dialogue skills. Responses rej analyzed ñan historical accuracy, empathy, im depth in inquiry. Higher-quality kajjitōk earn eḷap ḷọk XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Kwaḷọk ak ṇọṇak response suggestions im conversation hints. ñe enabled, eo system provides scaffolded kajjitōk starters, historical context naan in jiroñ, im engagement suggestions. Helpful ñan rūkkatak ekāāl ñan historical inquiry ak those needing support ippan kapeḷḷọk-ended questioning. rūkaki maroñ disable hints ñan eḷap ḷọk advanced assessment scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Display helpful hints ñan engaging ippan eo persona. Hints include historically relevant kajjitōk ñan ask, topics eo character would find interesting, im naan in jiroñ eṇ lead ñan deeper understanding. Eḷap ñan rūkkatak who need scaffolding ak aren't sure how ñan begin a historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Jilkinḷọk eo am message ñan eo persona character. eo am kajjitōk ak response ej analyzed ñan relevance im depth. Eo AI persona will respond authentically based ioon their historical context, knowledge, im personality. Well-crafted kajjitōk eṇ kwaḷọk historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Kiili eo persona conversation panel. eo am chat history im earned XP rej automatically saved. kwe maroñ resume in conversation later from eo History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Kiili Persona Chat",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Jeje eo am reflection ioon eo conversation ñan assessment. Reflect ioon ta kwe learned about eo historical figure, how their perspective differs from modern viewpoints, im how in conversation changed eo am understanding. Reflections rej evaluated using a rubric aligned ñan historical thinking skills im maroñ earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End eo conversation im generate a comprehensive summary in eo am discussion. Eo summary includes: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality in eo am kajjitōk, empathy demonstrated, im XP earned. in summary maroñ be exported ñan assessment, added ñan rūkkatak portfolios, ak used as a writing prompt ñan reflection activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Kōjparok in conversation ñan review ak share later. Saved chats preserve eo kadedeḷọk dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, im any reflections. Kōjerbal saved chats ñan rūkkatak portfolios, assessment kein kemool, kilaaj discussions, ak exemplar models. Saved conversations maroñ be exported as PDF ak shared ippan bar juon rūkkatak.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get a conversation starter ak topic suggestion ñe kwe're jab sure ta ñan ask. Eo system generates historically relevant kajjitōk based ioon eo persona's background, expertise, im iien period. Eḷap ñan overcoming writer's block ak discovering ekāāl angles ñan explore ilo eo am historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically jilkinḷọk eo am message ñe kwe bōjrak typing ñan a few sekōn. Creates a eḷap ḷọk natural conversational flow, especially ñe using voice dictation. Disable in if kwe prefer ñan review im ukot messages ṃokta sending, ak if kwe need eḷap ḷọk iien ñan compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Analyze eo am source text ñan reading level, complexity, im features.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check eo source content against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Generate a visual organizer from eo am source content.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Generate a timeline in events from eo am source content.",
    "timeline_topic": "Eo main topic ak theme in eo timeline being kōṃṃan. Eo AI creates historically accurate events based ioon in topic im eo am source content. Example topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle in Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events rej automatically ordered chronologically ñan sequencing practice.",
    "timeline_count": "nōṃba in events ñan include ilo eo timeline. eḷap ḷọk events create longer, eḷap ḷọk detailed timelines but increase difficulty. Recommended: 4-6 events ñan beginners, 8-10 ñan intermediate, 12+ ñan advanced rūkkatak. Events rej draggable ñan sequencing practice ālikin epepen.",
